INSTALLATION
============

Required dependencies
---------------------
On an apt-like distro, you'll need:
# apt-get install libmate-panel-applet-dev

On Arch linux:
# pacman -S autoconf automake make gcc pkg-config glib2 mate-panel

Compilation
-----------

$ ./autogen.sh
$ ./configure --prefix=/usr
$ make
$ sudo make install


UNINSTALL
========

$ make uninstall
